{"tid":1681050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登不停吹休息風","createTime":"2019-10-29T07:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T08:01:52.000Z","uid":249361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b234444f47bf84fe4e9296484bf6fb48c4acb655","tid":1681050,"uid":249361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"依幾個星期不停有人叫人休息 要和理非和平集會<br />\n唔知係咪想消磨大家既意志<br />\n香港人好善忘 個個星期都休息<br />\n好快就會習慣左唔出黎抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候做返d野喇勇武和理非們<br />\n112見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SnpkUYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSnpkUYs.jpg&h=0e6d30aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e5b9556a49f47f8831660494d2feff862e0526b","tid":1681050,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:27:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"c847d8a52e05667a814e6e0594477d345bea3991","tid":1681050,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"db7ccdf3dd942fbac624c0b401066e7dc93ff53f","tid":1681050,"uid":326414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfa40fe68afb3b8c3c5ccba49af3c4ce78b03e1d","tid":1681050,"uid":315584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite